snippet.title: UP9 | Game Trailer | TabTale
snippet.description:
Up 9 is the most addicting new puzzle game! Simply slide up numbered hexagons on the honey grid. Stack the same numbers to merge them up to 9.
Be smart when you stack pieces. The grid can get filled up very easily.
Up 9 is a fun and exciting block merge game, and you can play continuously for free! It is a simple puzzle game that will challenge you, while also training your brain.
 
HOW TO PLAY
• Drop hexagon numbers onto the honey grid
• Tap an item to rotate your game piece before dropping it.
• Form a higher number by merging three or more pieces of the same number.
• 9 is the final number, which is quite interesting. Try merging three 9’s and see what happens.
 
 
FEATURES
• Fun and easy to learn.
• Unlimited reloads, NO TIME LIMITS.
• Challenge your friends with your score.
• Play offline anytime.
• Eye-friendly colors.
 
Enjoy playing!


ABOUT US
Crazy Labs is a casual games brand, under which TabTale develops and publishes fun and addictive games. Crazy Labs partners with independent development studios across the globe to create engaging mobile content for audiences of all ages.
